Name: PKS_KR
Description: This enzymatic domain is part of bacterial polyketide synthases and catalyses the first step in the reductive modification of the beta-carbonyl centres in the growing polyketide chain. It uses NADPH to reduce the keto group to a hydroxy group.

Name: PKS_AT
Description: Acyl transferase domain in polyketide synthase (PKS) enzymes.
